metadata.name: Euphoria
metadata.description:
The festival of Holi, which is celebrated across India with great enthusiasm and joy. Holi is known as the festival of colors, where people smear each other with brightly colored powders and water. 

The festival celebrates the arrival of spring and the victory of good over evil. It is a time to forget past grudges and embrace each other with love and forgiveness.
